snippet.title: Best VGM 755 - StarFighter 3000 - Floating
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

3DO / Acorn Archimedes / Saturn / Playstation / PC
StarFighter 3000 (1996)
Floating
John Avery
